SUMMARY:Information: ELIZABETH LINE: Sunday 15 March\, until 0745\, no 
 service between Paddington and Ealing Broadway. Please use London 
 Underground connections. The Saturday evening 2345 Didcot Parkway to 
 London Paddington GWR train will finish its journey at Ealing Broadway. 
 The Sunday morning 0638 London Paddington to Reading GWR train will start 
 from Ealing Broadway and will run slightly later throughout. TfL Central 
 line connections will be available between Central London and Ealing 
 Broadway.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTAMP:20260315T055307Z
UID:3d2576f8-2033-11f1-bc25-7ced8d1e7c68
DTSTART:20260315
